the tv station also establish a reception group of 25 to receive donors .
a total of 210 million riyals ( us $ 56 million ) in cash and a large amount of materials have been amassed through this activity .
king of saudi arabia donated 10 million riyals ( us $ 2.67 million ) , crown prince abdullah donated 5 million riyals ( us $ 1.34 million ) and the well-known saudi arabian entrepreneur prince walid donated 100 million riyals ( us $ 26.7 million ) .
although the two days of 11th and 12th are holidays in saudi arabia and there were thunderstorms , cars were queuing up in front of the tv station waiting to donate .
many salary men from companies and enterprises donated one day of their wages .
east timor presidential election campaign ends
xinhua news agency report of april 12 from jakarta - local reports said the three week long east timor presidential election campaign wound up on the 12th .
the first president of the country , which will be declaring independence on may 20 , will be picked out by the voters on the 14th .
the two presidential candidates are xanana gusmao and xavier do amaral .
gusmao is leader of east timor 's independence movement while do amaral was president of the short-lived " democratic republic of east timor " founded in november 1975 .
