the new constitution will take effect from may 20 when east timor declares independence and the constituent assembly automatically becomes the first parliament .
foreign ministry spokeswoman confirms a chinese worker killed in jerusalem bombing attack
xinhua news agency report of april 13 from beijing - foreign ministry spokeswoman zhang qiyue confirmed today that a chinese worker was killed in a bombing attack in the afternoon of april 12 near a bus stop in jerusalem , and two other chinese workers wounded and another one missing .
zhang qiyue said the suicide bombing attack occurred at a bus stop in the city proper of jerusalem at about 4 p.m. on april 12 , killing 6 immediately and wounding over 70 .
a chinese worker died in the bombing attack , other two chinese workers wounded while another missing .
she said the chinese embassy to israel attached great importance to the incident and immediately sent officers to jerusalem with representatives of related companies to identify the victim , see the wounded workers , inquire about relevant circumstances and contact related parties to handle relief issues .
the embassy has in the same night notified chinese citizens and companies in israel to take care when getting outside .
she said chinese government extended its condolence to the chinese victims of the incident and their families .
china condemns violence targeting innocent civilians and appeals to palestine and israel for concrete actions to stop violence and restore peace to prevent more innocent deaths .
zhang qiyue said the chinese government reminds chinese citizens and those who plan to go to israel to take care when getting outside , keep in close touch with their families in china and contact the chinese embassy to israel immediately in case of emergency .
mideast news agency from egypt reported that foreign ministers of the two countries agreed in the telephone talks that israel should make positive response to the quartet statement of un , us , russia and eu issued in spain by withdrawing troops immediately from the palestinian territory .
mashel informed pique of his meeting with arafat on friday this week in the palestinian-controlled city of ramahla in west bank of jordan river .
mashel said palestine is prepared to seek for solution to the ending of israel 's invasion of palestinian territory according to relevant un resolutions in cooperation with the international community .
mashel and pique also agreed to remain in touch with related parties to work out solutions to completely end the mideast conflict .
