but an official from the us defence department who refused to be identified , said powell 's meeting with arafat may be postponed to the 14th .
reports said mashel made a telephone call with lebanon 's prime minister hariri the same day exchanging views on latest development of the palestinian situation .
uae declares to bear cost of jenin refugee camp restoration in palestine
