foreign ministry spokeswoman comments on report passed by european parliament
xinhua news agency report of april 19 from beijing - foreign ministry spokeswoman zhang qiyue made comments on a report passed by european parliament today when answering questions from journalists .
a journalist asked : on april 11 , the plenary session of the european parliament reviewed and passed the " report of the european parliament on european commission 's strategy document toward china " .
what comments does china have on this ?
