kidnapped indian senior commissioner agency staff to pakistan freed
xinhua news agency report of april 19 from new delhi ( by staff reporter xiong changyi ) - indian foreign ministry spokesman rao announced on the evening of 19th that kana , a staff member of india 's senior commissioner agency to pakistan who was kidnapped in the morning in pakistan 's capital city of islamabad was freed in the afternoon .
