his report last year received 1,873 votes for , 584 votes against and 332 abstentions .
as this year 's session is the last of this congress and a new congress is to be elected next year , yesterday 's closing convention also passed the " decision on the number of delegates to the 10th national people 's congress and issues relating to voting " , providing that the 10th national people 's congress shall be elected by the end of january next year .
